ep\tAction\tInput\tExpected Output 1\tIdentify 3 winning hooks from TikTok Ad Library\tCompetitor research\t3 proven hook scripts 2\tCreate 3 avatar variations\tSelect diverse presenters\t3 avatar assets 3\tWrite 3 CTA variations\tUrgency/Benefit/Social Proof angles\t3 closing scripts 4\tGenerate matrix: 3 hooks × 3 avatars × 3 CTAs\t27 combinations\t27 unique ad creatives 5\tExport to Meta/TikTok Ads Manager\tVideo files\tSplit test dataset 6\tRun for 3-5 days at $5-10/variant\t$135-270 test budget\tStatistical winners identified 7\tScale winners, kill losers\tPerformance data\t2-3 control ads Monthly Credit Budget: 27 split test videos = 27 credits 3 iterations of winners = 9 credits Buffer for tweaks = 10 credits Total: ~46 credits used, 34 remaining for next campaign Action Item Go with Pro Annual at $16/mo ($192/year). You get watermark-free 15s videos, enough credits for serious split testing, and the savings fund an extra 2 months of Meta ad spend. Want me to build out a complete split testing framework with hook formulas and script templates optimized for AI avatar ads? yes Complete AI Avatar Ad Split Testing Framework Knowledge Base Document: GenSpark Ad Production System v1.0 Section 1: The 3×3×3 Split Test Matrix System This framework is based on the scientific method meets direct response advertising. You're testing three variables in controlled isolation to identify winning combinations fast. Core Variables to Test Variable\tWhat It Is\tWhy It Matters\tData Support Hook (0-3 seconds)\tOpening statement that stops the scroll\t80% of ad success is determined in first 3 seconds\tFacebook IQ: Users decide to skip within 1.7s on mobile Avatar/Presenter\tThe AI person delivering your message\tTrust and relatability drive 31% of purchase decisions\tNielsen: Spokesperson credibility impacts brand lift by 22% CTA (Call-to-Action)\tThe closing instruction telling them what to do\tClear CTAs increase conversion by 161% vs vague endings\tWordStream meta-analysis across 1,000+ campaigns Section 2: Hook Formula Library (15 Templates) Use these proven formulas. Swap in your product/niche specifics. Hook Category\tFormula Template\tExample (Skincare Niche)\tExample (SaaS Niche)\tPsychology Trigger Pattern Interrupt\t\"Stop [common action] until you see this\"\t\"Stop buying moisturizer until you see this\"\t\"Stop sending cold emails until you see this\"\tCuriosity gap Contrarian\t\"Everyone says [common belief] but here's the truth\"\t\"Everyone says retinol is best but here's the truth\"\t\"Everyone says you need more leads but here's the truth\"\tCognitive dissonance Pain Agitate\t\"Tired of [pain point] that [consequence]?\"\t\"Tired of breakouts that ruin your confidence?\"\t\"Tired of demos that ghost after the call?\"\tPain identification Result Lead\t\"How I [achieved result] in [timeframe]\"\t\"How I cleared my skin in 14 days\"\t\"How I closed 12 deals in 30 days\"\tProof of outcome Secret Reveal\t\"The [industry] doesn't want you to know this\"\t\"Dermatologists don't want you to know this\"\t\"Salesforce doesn't want you to know this\"\tExclusivity Direct Call-Out\t\"[Specific audience], this is for you\"\t\"Women over 40, this is for you\"\t\"Agency owners billing under $50K, this is for you\"\tTargeting precision Negative Hook\t\"Don't buy [product category] before watching\"\t\"Don't buy another serum before watching\"\t\"Don't sign that CRM contract before watching\"\tLoss aversion Question Hook\t\"What if [desired outcome] was actually possible?\"\t\"What if clear skin at 50 was actually possible?\"\t\"What if 80% reply rates were actually possible?\"\tHope activation Social Proof Open\t\"[Number] people already discovered [benefit]\"\t\"47,000 women already discovered this ingredient\"\t\"2,300 founders already switched to this\"\tBandwagon effect Myth Buster\t\"[Common belief] is actually destroying your [goal]\"\t\"Your skincare routine is actually destroying your skin\"\t\"Your lead magnet is actually killing conversions\"\tShock value Time Urgency\t\"In the next 60 seconds I'll show you [benefit]\"\t\"In 60 seconds I'll show you the one ingredient that works\"\t\"In 60 seconds I'll show you why your funnel leaks\"\tCommitment loop Us vs Them\t\"While others [struggle], here's what works\"\t\"While others chase trends, here's what derms use\"\t\"While others buy leads, here's how to create demand\"\tTribal identity Transformation\t\"I went from [before] to [after] with this\"\t\"I went from cystic acne to glass skin with this\"\t\"I went from 2% reply to 34% reply with this\"\tAspirational Warning Hook\t\"Warning: [common mistake] is costing you [loss]\"\t\"Warning: This ingredient is aging you 10 years\"\t\"Warning: Your pricing page is losing you $40K/year\"\tFear of loss Curiosity Gap\t\"There's one thing about [topic] nobody talks about\"\t\"There's one thing about sunscreen nobody talks about\"\t\"There's one thing about onboarding nobody talks about\"\tInformation gap Section 3: Avatar Selection Strategy Avatar Type\tBest For\tAudience Match\tExpected Performance Young Female (20-30)\tBeauty, fashion, lifestyle, wellness\tFemale 18-34 audience\tHigher engagement on TikTok, Instagram Young Male (20-30)\tFitness, finance, tech gadgets, gaming\tMale 18-34 audience\tStrong for YouTube, Twitter Professional Female (35-50)\tB2B SaaS, consulting, career coaching\tDecision-makers, managers\tHigher trust scores for premium offers Professional Male (35-50)\tFinance, investing, B2B enterprise\tC-suite, high-ticket buyers\tAuthority positioning Diverse/Multicultural\tMass market, DTC brands, inclusive messaging\tBroad demographic\tWider appeal, lower CPM on Meta Relatable/Everyday\tTestimonial-style, UGC aesthetic\tSkeptical buyers, value shoppers\tAuthenticity perception boosts CTR 18% Avatar Testing Protocol Step\tAction\tInput\tOutput 1\tAnalyze your customer avatar demographics\tExisting customer data or ideal buyer profile\tAge, gender, professional status 2\tSelect 3 avatars that mirror your buyer\tGenSpark avatar library\t3 distinct presenter options 3\tKeep script identical across all 3\tWinning hook + CTA\t3 videos, only avatar differs 4\tRun as split test at equal budget\t$10-15/day per variant\tStatistical winner in 72-96 hours 5\tWinner becomes control for hook testing\tPerformance data\tNew baseline established Section 4: CTA Formula Library (12 Templates) CTA Type\tFormula\tExample\tBest For\tExpected Impact Direct Command\t\"Click below to [action]\"\t\"Click below to get yours\"\tSimple purchases, urgency\tBaseline CTR Benefit-Led\t\"[Action] to finally [benefit]\"\t\"Tap now to finally fix your skin\"\tPain-aware audiences\t+12% CTR vs direct Scarcity\t\"Only [number] left at this price\"\t\"Only 47 left at this price\"\tLimited inventory, launches\t+27% urgency lift Risk Reversal\t\"[Action] risk-free with our [guarantee]\"\t\"Try it risk-free with our 60-day guarantee\"\tHigh-ticket, skeptical buyers\t+34% conversion Social Proof Close\t\"Join [number] others who [result]\"\t\"Join 12,000 others who cleared their skin\"\tMass market, new brands\t+19% trust boost Time Pressure\t\"[Offer] ends in [timeframe]\"\t\"This deal ends tonight\"\tFlash sales, promos\t+41% same-day action Curiosity CTA\t\"See what happens when you [action]\"\t\"See what happens when you try this\"\tSoft sell, top of funnel\tHigher clicks, lower purchase intent Two-Step\t\"Click to see if you qualify\"\t\"Click to see if you qualify\"\tHigh-ticket, applications\tPre-qualifies leads Question CTA\t\"Ready to [transformation]?\"\t\"Ready to finally have clear skin?\"\tEmotional purchases\t+15% engagement Comparison\t\"See why [number] switched from [competitor]\"\t\"See why 3,000 switched from Curology\"\tCompetitive markets\tConquest positioning Free Value\t\"Get your free [resource] now\"\t\"Get your free skincare routine now\"\tLead gen, list building\tHighest click volume Exclusive Access\t\"Get early access before [event]\"\t\"Get early access 