ed, dermatologist approved\"\tSocial proof + authority CTA\t12-15s\t\"Tap below to try it risk-free with our 60-day guarantee\"\tRisk Reversal formula Section 7: Production Workflow SOP Step-by-Step GenSpark Production Step\tAction\tWhere to Click\tInput Required\tExpected Output\tTime 1\tLog into GenSpark\tgenspark.ai → Login\tEmail/password\tDashboard access\t30s 2\tClick \"Create Video\"\tMain dashboard → Create Video button\tNone\tVideo editor opens\t10s 3\tSelect Avatar\tLeft panel → Avatars tab → Browse\tClick preferred avatar from library\tAvatar selected, preview shows\t1 min 4\tEnter Script\tCenter panel → Script text box\tPaste your 15s script\tText appears in editor\t30s 5\tSelect Voice\tRight panel → Voice dropdown\tChoose voice matching avatar\tVoice assigned\t30s 6\tPreview\tBottom bar → Preview button\tNone\t15s preview renders\t1-2 min 7\tAdjust Pacing\tScript panel → Pause markers\tAdd [pause] tags if needed\tNatural delivery\t2 min 8\tGenerate Video\tTop right → Generate button\tConfirm 1 credit use\tVideo renders\t3-5 min 9\tDownload\tMy Videos → Select → Download\tChoose MP4 1080p\tVideo file saved\t30s 10\tRename File\tLocal folder → Right click → Rename\tUse code: H1-A1-C1.mp4\tOrganized file system\t10s Batch Production Schedule Day\tTask\tVideos to Produce\tCredits Used\tCumulative Monday\tHook 1 + All Avatar/CTA combos\tV01-V09\t9\t9 Tuesday\tHook 2 + All Avatar/CTA combos\tV10-V18\t9\t18 Wednesday\tHook 3 + All Avatar/CTA combos\tV19-V27\t9\t27 Thursday\tReview, make tweaks, reshoot fails\t2-5 fixes\t5\t32 Friday\tUpload to ad platforms\t0 production\t0\t32 Section 8: Ad Platform Upload & Testing Setup Meta Ads Manager Setup Step\tAction\tNavigation Path\tInput\tOutput 1\tCreate Campaign\tAds Manager → Create → Campaign\tSelect \"Sales\" or \"Traffic\" objective\tCampaign created 2\tSet Budget\tCampaign level → Budget\t$10-15/day per ad set during test\tBudget locked 3\tCreate Ad Sets\tAd Set level → Duplicate 27x\tOne ad set per video vari